1 - spawned Inoshishi
2 - agreed to help
3 - Inoshishi spawns at the Temple of Wisdom
4 - agreed to track bandit
5 - party returned amulet, gallena does some divination
6 - divination done, have post-talk with ino
7 - ino moves back outside
8 - asked to find both parts of blade
9 - returned both parts to ino
10 - spawned ino at taerom's
11 - taerom's started work, ino leaves
    CDMonkCallingPaid or CDMonkCallingNotPaid set to 1
    CDMonkCallingBladeTime timer set for 4 days
12 - spawn ino if timer expired
13 - taerom forging cutscene complete, prompt final dialogue
14 - ino rewards player, rides off into the sunset with the sword
15 - player convinces ino to also give him the sword, quest ends
16 - ino rewards player, player demands sword and kills ino for it
*/

